dct_title_s: CARTE Particuliere du Golphe de Mexique et des Antisles
dct_description_sm: No named engraver, and pagination changed to: "I.Deel. pag.1." (top right).
California as an island with flat northern coast sloping up to east, and with C. Blanc, C. Mendocina, C. de Pinas, and C. S. Lucas labelled. Mainland coastline continues north.
Issued in: Nouveaux voyages / J.B. Labat, The Hague, 1724. Reissued in the Paris edition, 1742.
